-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm h-full hover:shadow-md transition-all cursor-pointer group hover:border-emerald-200\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg text-emerald-600 bg-emerald-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-eye h-6 w-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.062 12.348a1 1 0 0 1 0-.696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1 19.876 0 1 1 0 0 1 0 .696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1-19.876 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Proof Cam</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\">Capture timestamped, watermarked photos as evidence for transactions.</p></div></div></a><a href=\"/tools/escrow\"><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm h-full hover:shadow-md transition-all cursor-pointer group hover:border-emerald-200\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg text-cyan-600 bg-cyan-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-6 w-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Escrow Protection</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\">Secure your payments with our escrow system. Funds released only after verification.</p></div></div></a></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\